  "name": "Staff of Frost",
  "type": "weapon",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<div class=\"item-attunement\"><i>(Requires attunement by a Druid, Sorcerer, Warlock, or Wizard)</i></div><p>You have resistance to &amp;Reference[cold]{cold} damage while you hold this staff.</p>\n<p>The staff has 10 charges. While holding it, you can use an action to expend 1 or more of its charges to cast one of the following spells from it, using your spell save DC: <strong></strong>@UUID[Compendium.world.ddb-lost-mines-phandelver-spells.Item.JZY4U6j4RPYzapxo]{cone of cold} (5 charges), <strong></strong>@UUID[Compendium.world.ddb-lost-mines-phandelver-spells.Item.HYyb02Wcy1APER0i]{fog cloud} (1 charge), <strong></strong>@UUID[Compendium.world.ddb-lost-mines-phandelver-spells.Item.ai7yGMLr02BEP3qV]{ice storm} (4 charges), or <strong></strong>@UUID[Compendium.world.ddb-lost-mines-phandelver-spells.Item.riGu62YXb6HfDQZx]{wall of ice} (4 charges).</p>\n<p>The staff regains 1d6 + 4 expended charges daily at dawn. If you expend the last charge, roll a d20. On a 1, the staff turns to water and is destroyed.</p>\n</div>",
      "chat": ""
    },
